<i>Lieutenant Commander,</i>
<i>the Honorable Ewen Montagu...</i>


1204
01:40:45.174 --> 01:40:49.132
<i>Royal Naval Volunteer Reserve.</i>

1205
01:41:02.122 --> 01:41:04.925
<i>Lieutenant Commander John Adams...</i>

1206
01:41:04.960 --> 01:41:08.918
<i>Royal Navy.</i>

1207
01:41:09.496 --> 01:41:12.066
<i>Lieutenant Commander David Hebden...</i>

1208
01:41:12.101 --> 01:41:16.059
<i>Royal Navy.</i>

1209
01:41:17.671 --> 01:41:20.741
<i>Can you assure me, 
Commander Montagu...</i>

1210
01:41:20.776 --> 01:41:23.242
<i>as an officer and a gentleman...</i>

1211
01:41:23.277 --> 01:41:26.914
<i>that this thing</i>
<i>you are going to do is good...</i>


1212
01:41:26.949 --> 01:41:29.949
<i>and worthy of him...</i>

1213
01:41:29.984 --> 01:41:32.751
<i>that if I agree to your request...</i>

1214
01:41:32.786 --> 01:41:36.779
<i>my son's body will be treated</i>
<i>decently and with respect...</i>


1215
01:41:38.125 --> 01:41:42.118
<i>and that finally</i>
<i>he will have Christian burial?</i>


1216
01:42:39.320 --> 01:42:41.655
<i>Last night I dreamed...</i>

1217
01:42:41.690 --> 01:42:43.789
<i>a deadly dream.</i>

1218
01:42:43.824 --> 01:42:46.977
<i>Beyond the Isle of Skye...</i>

1219
01:42:47.012 --> 01:42:50.130
<i>I saw a dead man win a fight...</i>

1220
01:42:50.165 --> 01:42:54.123
<i>and I think that man was I.</i>

